<h1>Update Personal Information</h1>

<p>System administrators can update a person's personal information in the radiology information system.</p>
<p>Select a person and click the "<span class="code">GO</span>" button. System administrators will be able to manage personal information of this person. </p>

<p>You can change any of the following fields:</p>

<ul>
	<li>First Name</li>
	<li>Last Name</li>
	<li>Address</li>
	<li>Email*</li>
	<li>Phone</li>
	<li>Password</li>
</ul>

<p><span class="code">* Note that the Email should be unique, which means that a person cannot have the same Email with any other perseon in our database.</span></p>

<p>Click the "<span class="code">OK</span>" button to save the changes.</p>

